Class DefaultSubscription

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.betfair.cougar.core.impl.ev.DefaultSubscription
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Subscription

    public class DefaultSubscription
extends Object
implements Subscription
    Utility default subscription class which handles listener interaction. Any subclass wanting to trigger specific functionality around closure should override either preClose(CloseReason) or postClose(CloseReason) as appropriate.
